snippet.title: Hellscreen Kickstarter launch trailer
snippet.description:
Hellscreen is a single player level based first-person shooter for PC, in the fast, frantic style of classic FPS games from the 1990s (such as Doom, Quake, Unreal etc).

-------------------------
Coming to Kickstarter  27th February 2019

Back here:

https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/171000943/hellscreen-90s-style-fps-video-game

-------------------------
